  "original_title": "\u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0, \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Notification of dates for Higher, Ordinary and Scholarship Examinations",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has issued a notification regarding the dates for the general higher, ordinary and scholarship examinations for the year 2022.",
        "In that way, the Ministry of Education has decided to conduct the Higher Level Examinations for the year 2022 from the 28th of November to the 23rd of December.",
        "Also, it is worth noting that the Ministry of Education has also announced that the scholarship exam for this year will be held on November 27, and the ordinary level exam for 2022 will be held in April and May 2023."
      ],
